summary:
A highly motivated geoscience young professional, eager to learn and apply new skills to tackle challenging problems in the field of petroleum geoscience. Adaptable, enthusiastic, a self starter whether it means working under pressure, in a team or individually. Strong interpersonal skills, cooperative and supportive to fellow teams members.

Specialist areas: 
Basin Analysis
Fluid flow, hydrocarbon leakage and sequestration;
Marine gas hydrates;
2D, 3D and seismic interpretation;
Structural analysis;
Seismic attribute extraction and analysis;
